\b\fs24 Recommendations\b0\fs22\par
\par
1. Immediate suspension of Officer Michael Brown without pay, effective immediately.\par
2. Initiation of termination proceedings per department policy Section 14.2.\par
3. Referral to the District Attorney's office for review of criminal charges.\par
4. Mandatory retraining for all patrol officers on de-escalation techniques and use of force continuum.\par
